    dialogue:
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: Now that's sad.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: It's really not that hard. The players will actually
        PAY you not to die.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: We have no use for girls who can't even stay alive.
        Sorry, Asuka, you won't make it here.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: And to think that we actually had high expectations
        of you.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
